WEBVTT
Kind: captions
Language: en

00:00:01.233 --> 00:00:02.566
- IT'S TIME TO COVER
THE WORLD OF FASHION

00:00:02.566 --> 00:00:03.800
IN OUR SEGMENT "HOT GLAM, GIRL."

00:00:03.800 --> 00:00:05.500
[energetic pop music]

00:00:05.500 --> 00:00:08.500
[cheers and applause]

00:00:12.333 --> 00:00:14.833
- HOT GLAM, GIRL!

00:00:14.833 --> 00:00:16.333
[laughter]

00:00:16.333 --> 00:00:18.333
- ALL RIGHT,
THIS COMES FROM LAUREN JAMESON

00:00:18.333 --> 00:00:19.666
IN ANNISTON, ALABAMA.

00:00:19.666 --> 00:00:20.900
"HI, ELLEN, I REMEMBER THINKING

00:00:20.900 --> 00:00:22.400
"HOW BEAUTIFUL
MY SISTER AND I LOOKED

00:00:22.400 --> 00:00:24.533
WHEN WE TOOK THESE
PICTURES WITH MY NANA."

00:00:24.533 --> 00:00:28.166
[laughter]

00:00:28.166 --> 00:00:31.000
WELL, SOME WOMEN KEEP KLEENEX
TUCKED IN THEIR BLOUSE.

00:00:31.000 --> 00:00:32.333
SHE KEEPS HER GRANDDAUGHTERS.

00:00:32.333 --> 00:00:35.333
[laughter]

00:00:35.333 --> 00:00:37.933
ROBIN MILLER
IN SAN PEDRO, CALIFORNIA.

00:00:37.933 --> 00:00:39.333
"HERE'S A PHOTO
I TOOK IN THE '90s.

00:00:39.333 --> 00:00:41.033
"THE STYLIST THOUGHT
IT WOULD BE A GOOD IDEA

00:00:41.033 --> 00:00:42.366
TO ADD TISSUE PAPER."

00:00:42.366 --> 00:00:48.333
[laughter]

00:00:48.333 --> 00:00:49.633
YOU KNOW WHAT?

00:00:49.633 --> 00:00:50.833
THAT LOOKS FAMILIAR.

00:00:50.833 --> 00:00:52.666
CAN WE PAN OUT,
AND LET'S SEE WHERE SHE IS.

00:00:52.666 --> 00:00:55.000
OH, SHE'S IN THERE.
[laughter]

00:00:55.000 --> 00:00:57.666
SHE'S IN NANA'S OUTFIT.

00:00:57.666 --> 00:00:59.333
[laughter and applause]

00:00:59.333 --> 00:01:00.666
[chuckles]

00:01:02.333 --> 00:01:04.933
BERNETTE GUTIERREZ
IN LOS ANGELES, CALIFORNIA.

00:01:04.933 --> 00:01:06.833
"I TOOK THIS PICTURE
WITH TWO OF MY BEST FRIENDS.

00:01:06.833 --> 00:01:08.300
WE STILL JOKE ABOUT IT."

00:01:08.300 --> 00:01:11.500
[laughter]

00:01:11.500 --> 00:01:12.500
OH.

00:01:15.833 --> 00:01:17.666
NO.

00:01:17.666 --> 00:01:20.500
THAT'S NICE.

00:01:20.500 --> 00:01:22.000
YOU CAN TELL
THEY'RE BEST FRIENDS.

00:01:22.000 --> 00:01:23.666
LOOK AT THE LOVE.
YOU FEEL THE LOVE.

00:01:23.666 --> 00:01:26.500
[laughter]

00:01:26.500 --> 00:01:30.666
[chuckles]

00:01:30.666 --> 00:01:32.666
THIS WOMAN'S NAME
IS NARI CHERRY.

00:01:32.666 --> 00:01:35.333
NARI CHERRY,
SANTA CLARITA, CALIFORNIA.

00:01:35.333 --> 00:01:37.166
"MY FRIEND POSTED THIS
ON HER FACEBOOK PAGE.

00:01:37.166 --> 00:01:38.500
I HAD TO SEND IT IN."

00:01:39.533 --> 00:01:41.066
[laughter]

00:01:41.066 --> 00:01:42.833
I DON'T THINK THERE'S ANYTHING
WRONG WITH THAT, HONESTLY.

00:01:42.833 --> 00:01:44.566
I DON'T--'CAUSE PORTIA AND I

00:01:44.566 --> 00:01:46.000
TOOK A PICTURE
VERY SIMILAR TO THAT.

00:01:46.000 --> 00:01:48.000
AND I DON'T THINK
THERE'S ANYTHING WRONG WITH IT.

00:01:48.000 --> 00:01:50.666
[laughter]

00:01:50.666 --> 00:01:52.666
OKAY,
THANKS FOR SENDING THOSE IN.

00:01:52.666 --> 00:01:54.100
IF YOU HAVE A HOT GLAM PHOTO

00:01:54.100 --> 00:01:55.666
YOU THINK I SHOULD SEE,
SEND IT TO ME.

00:01:55.666 --> 00:01:56.833
WE'LL BE BACK.

00:01:56.833 --> 00:01:59.833
[cheers and applause]

